snippet.title: 散歩 - Walk (All Endings, Secret Ending) A J-Horror game where a schoolgirl is stalked by a monster!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://hauntedps1.itch.io/demodisc2021?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt A third-person, J-Horror experience! Play as a girl walking to home from school. It's getting dark, and something is out to get you!

This re-upload includes both endings (ending 1 and the secret ending). The secret ending is accessible by typing in the word "CHANNEL2" using your keyboard while standing in front of the television. https://itch.io/t/1286327/-walk-endings-spoilers?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
